Nicola Stephenson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicola_Stephenson 0 Nicola Stephenson (born 5 July 1971) is an English actress. She played the roles of Margaret Clemence in Brookside, Julie Fitzjohn in Holby City, Sarah Williams in The Chase and Tess Harris in Emmerdale.
